## Data Flow

```
Frontend (45s interval)
    ↓ fetch('/api/market')
Vercel Serverless Function
    ↓ Yahoo Finance v7/v8 API
    ↓ (30s server cache)
    ↓ Returns structured JSON
Frontend
    ↓ marketToNERVA() parameter mapping
    ↓ NERVA.classify() quantum engine
    ↓ Render decision state
```

